name: ICONS: Twiggy
description:
Canvas print, mounted, 100 x 120 cm (4 cm deep). Limited edition of 2. Signed by me. 

Worldwide shipping. Can be personally delivered in the Stockholm city area, free of charge. 

‘ICONS’ is a series of portraits of people who somehow have achieved iconic status for different reasons. The portraits are composed of a mosaic of small icons, that have been carefully selected and represent different events and themes from the peoples' lives and activities. The technology behind the images is a bit of digital stenciling and nothing has been done automatically; a very tiresome but rewarding process.
